content: META-DREAMER: Drove a significant architectural update this month by implementing a multi-repository frontend in elizaos/elizaos.github.io via PR #143, a substantial effort adding over 11k lines of code. This work, which originated from their own issue #141, was followed by a massive cleanup initiative that removed over 258k lines of legacy scripts and data in PR #145. Their activity shows a primary focus on new feature development, testing, and large-scale refactoring, touching a mix of code, test, and configuration files.
